QuantumToys.client

Class SchroedingerWebApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • QuantumToys.client.SchroedingerWebApp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.gwt.core.client.EntryPoint

    public class SchroedingerWebApp
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.gwt.core.client.EntryPoint
    This is the entry point for the web application. It solves the Schroedinger equation and shows results on the web. This is only the interface, while the actual equation solving code is in QuantumToys.shared.SchroedingerCalculator.
    Author:
    Danilo Ferreira de Lima
    See Also:
    SchroedingerCalculator
